ja|Haro]] was put on lockdown.<ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/mar/07/spanish-town-faces-police-lockdown-to-contain-coronavirus Spanish town faces police lockdown to contain coronavirus] The Guardian</ref>\n\n;8 March\n* Seven more people were confirmed to have died.<ref name=ELMUNDO>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elmundo.es/ciencia-y-salud/salud/2020/03/08/5e6492d621efa0ab448b45f6.html|title=Coronavirus, \u00faltima hora {{!}} Siete nuevas muertes en Madrid, Zaragoza y Pa\u00eds Vasco elevan a 17 las v\u00edctimas mortales|author1=Sara Polo|author2=Marif\u00e9 Velasco|date=8 March 2020|orig-year=17:59|website=Elmundo|language=es|access-date=8 March 2020|url-status=usurped|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200308170056/https://www.elmundo.es/ciencia-y-salud/salud/2020/03/08/5e6492d621efa0ab448b45f6.html|archive-date=8 March 2020}} \u2013 {{Cite web|url=https://www.elmundo.es/ciencia-y-salud/salud/2020/03/08/5e6492d621efa0ab448b45f6.html|title=Coronavirus, \u00faltima hora {{!}} Contagiado un beb\u00e9 de cinco meses en Murcia|author1=Sara Polo|author2=Marif\u00e9 Velasco|date=9 March 2020|orig-year=00:49|website=Elmundo|language=es|access-date=9 March 2020|url-status=live|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200309000238/https://www.elmundo.es/ciencia-y-salud/salud/2020/03/08/5e6492d621efa0ab448b45f6.html|archive-date=9 March 2020}}</ref>\n* First case diagnosed in the [[Region of Murcia]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.murcia.com/noticias/2020/03/08-se-confirma-el-primer-caso-de-coronavirus-en-la-region.asp|title=Se confirma el primer caso de coronavirus en la Regi\u00f3n de Murcia - murcia.com|website=murcia.com|access-date=8 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n;9 March\n* The confirmed cases rose to 1,231 and the death toll to 30.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://elpais.com/sociedad/2020-03-09/ultimas-noticias-del-coronavirus-en-directo.html|title=\u00daltimas noticias del coronavirus, en directo |website=elpais.com|date=2 March 2020 |access-date=9 March 2020